# Project Overrides Template

## How To Use

- Copy this file into a target repository at `.cursor/rules/project-overrides.mdc`.
- Add only project-specific guidance here.
- Do not duplicate organization-wide rules from shared base files.
- If any project rule conflicts with shared rules, this project override is authoritative for this repository.

## Recommended Sections

- Architecture constraints specific to this project.
- Naming conventions specific to this project.
- Testing requirements specific to this project.
- Deployment or runtime constraints specific to this project.
